        <mxCell id="hVdRD_jrGuo00WOVqpVs-115" value="The master (Member 1) uses its interface address (192.168.1.10) for Grid communications with Member 6 and its NAT address (10.1.1.10) when communicating with the other Grid members. Member 6 uses its interface address (192.168.1.60) when communicating with the master. If Member 3 (a Master Candidate) ever became the Grid Master, then both Members 1 and 6 would use their NAT addresses when communicating with it." style="text;strokeColor=none;align=left;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
